ZH: 我们去清真寺祷告。
EN: We went to the mosque to pray.

ZH: 这座清真寺建于十七世纪。
EN: This mosque was built in the 17th century.

ZH: 清真寺是伊斯兰教徒的宗教场所。
EN: The mosque is a place of worship for Muslims.

ZH: 这座清真寺是城市的地标之一。
EN: This mosque is one of the landmarks of the city.

ZH: 我们每周都会去清真寺做礼拜。
EN: We go to the mosque for prayers every week.

ZH: 清真寺里的装饰非常漂亮。
EN: The decorations in the mosque are very beautiful.

ZH: 清真寺的塔楼可以远远的看到。
EN: The minaret of the mosque can be seen from far away.

ZH: 清真寺的宗教仪式非常庄严。
EN: The religious ceremonies in the mosque are very solemn.

ZH: 清真寺的大门上方悬挂着月牙标志。
EN: The crescent symbol hangs above the entrance of the mosque.

ZH: 清真寺是伊斯兰文化的重要组成部分。
EN: The mosque is an important part of Islamic culture.

ZH: 清真寺的穹顶是其建筑特色之一。
EN: The dome of the mosque is one of its architectural features.

ZH: 我们在清真寺举行了一场婚礼仪式。
EN: We held a wedding ceremony in the mosque.

ZH: 清真寺每天都会播放宣礼。
EN: The mosque plays the call to prayer every day.

ZH: 清真寺里的人们都很虔诚。
EN: The people in the mosque are all very devout.

ZH: 清真寺的地板上铺着厚厚的祈祷垫。
EN: The floor of the mosque is covered with thick prayer mats.

ZH: 清真寺的建筑风格融合了传统和现代元素。
EN: The architectural style of the mosque combines traditional and modern elements.

ZH: 清真寺里有一个教育中心用来传授伊斯兰教知识。
EN: The mosque has an educational center for teaching Islamic knowledge.

ZH: 清真寺每年都会举办宗教节日庆祝活动。
EN: The mosque holds religious festival celebrations every year.

ZH: 清真寺的礼拜堂可以容纳数百人。
EN: The prayer hall of the mosque can accommodate hundreds of people.

ZH: 清真寺是伊斯兰社区聚集的地方。
EN: The mosque is the gathering place for the Islamic community.
